"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T14:04:12.000Z","msg":"主控盤問時，指被告既然帶警察遊花園，會否同樣如此對待他。被告稱不會，因主控沒有說她濫交，加上她現已成熟；主控隨即問她：「咁你有冇濫交？」被告即輕聲答：「冇。」<br />\n<br />\n唔知佢有冇帶主控遊花園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aacec98ce26a5851393c07f6a6f87e769cbb5943","tid":757041,"uid":164913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T14:04:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"54ea1e399f570cd914beac702e1979482e40ea79","tid":757041,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9aaeda39648dc441c20da3e2e93799c9a8cbc2a","tid":757041,"uid":34189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6afe4f1a968596868c4a492eda0851bfe976b76f","tid":757041,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d40be716e32811c2fcea4d4f1c57c9e31688a611","tid":757041,"uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T13:34:16.000Z","msg":"「主控，你再問呢D問題，我又會忍唔住笑。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T13:53:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T13:59:40.000Z","msg":"如果佢轉數再高d串返個主控就正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T14:16:49.000Z","msg":"如果佢唔係被告<br />\n<br />\n係證人<br />\n<br />\n我估佢真係會寸主控"},{"pid":"e24e768db8ddd4b054877666bcf2a55b7d26347f","tid":757041,"uid":67500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T14:42:55.000Z","msg":"隔離post有全相，條女踢開足球隊"},{"pid":"7a5b7cf33a586a756d84281534df78f0532522bb","tid":757041,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T14:47:11.000Z","msg":"連登仔分分鐘又精神分裂<br />\n條女VS黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkg